What we have:
- function for calculating principal axes (.principal_Axes())
- function for density

What we want to do:
 - Load the trajectory
 - Select the helix and calculate princ. axis
 - Calculate distances with respect to this axis
 - Calculate 2D coordinates wrt this axis
 - Bin the distances/Coordinates
 - Create a histogram/density plot
 

Possibly useful stuff:
- Gromax gmx bundle: http://manual.gromacs.org/programs/gmx-bundle.html
